{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ff74cc8b53","title":"对黄永胜与“广州工联”造反派座谈时讲话摘要的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"199eca2246","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":23,"articleId":"ff74cc8b53","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"黄永胜","id":"440b5f1bc1","type":"人物"},{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"军队和军事","id":"6f7a683373","type":"主题"},{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[{"id":"206fbf26a3","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ff74cc8b53","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中共中央文化革命小组办事组1967年5月21日编印的《信电快报》第一三一期上。这期快报登载了中国人民解放军广州军区司今员黄永胜、副司今员温玉成等5月10日与“广州工联”8名造反派代表座谈时讲话的一部分。黄永胜在讲话中检查了“前一段支左工作中的缺点和错误，表示彻底给被打击迫害的革命造反派平反，坚决站在革命造反派一边”。"},{"id":"216de7004a","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ff74cc8b53","publication":{},"article":{},"index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"林彪，当时任中共中央军委副主席，在中共八届十一中全会上继续当选为中央政治局常委，不久被称中央副主席。恩来，即周恩来。"}],"contents":[{"id":"7ead3cd254","type":"title","text":"对黄永胜与“广州工联”造反派座谈时讲话摘要的批语！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ff74cc8b53","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"206fbf26a3","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪、恩来叫同志，并告文革小组：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ff74cc8b53","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"216de7004a","type":"paragraph","text":"黄永胜同志讲话一篇，建议发给各大军区，各省军区，各军，各军种兵种作为参考。我觉得这种小型的谈心会很好。当地最高首长出面与小将平等地谈心，不摆架子，有错爽直承认，而不谷谷叶吐，并且立即改正，这些都很好。如同意，请的处。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ff74cc8b53","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"de354322cf","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ff74cc8b53","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eb923e6ff8","type":"paragraph","text":"五月二十三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"ff74cc8b53","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":479,"end":479}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"61b3de30e2","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪、恩来同志，并告文革小组：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ff74cc8b53","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c6a7fc2d9b","type":"title","text":"对黄永胜与“广州工联”造反派座谈时讲话摘要的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ff74cc8b53","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f0b84f57cb","type":"paragraph","text":"黄永胜同志讲话一篇，建议发给各大军区，各省军区，各军、各军种兵种作为参考。我觉得这种小型的谈心会很好。当地最高首长出面与小将平等地谈心，不摆架子，有错爽直承认，而不吞吞吐吐，并且立即改正，这些都很好。如同意，请酌处。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ff74cc8b53","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}